formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1. This certificate is being issued for RERA compliance for the Divyajivan Infrastructure Private Limited (City) and is based on the records and documents produced before me and explanations provided to me by the management of the Company; based on the verification of unaudited provisional books of accounts till 31st May, 2022.
2. In some of the cases Unit Amount of Consideration is taken on the basis of Allotment Letter, the consideration in such units is subject to change till execution of conveyance deed.
3. In some of the cases where Sale Deed is executed without Agreement to Sale, Date of Sale Deed is taken as the Date of Agreement to Sale.
4. In case of units booked during the period under review allotee details including KYC and contact details and consideration value are considered on the basis of representation made by the promoter as the promoter is not in position to produce documentary evidence for verification.
5. Point 8 shows that the promoter drawn excess fund from RERA Bank Account than actual eligibility.  However, the promoter deposited 100% collection in RERA Bank Account though only 70% was required to be deposited, so the amount withdrawn till date of this certificate is in excess of net amount which can be withdrawn from the designated bank account.
6. Estimated cost is as certified by the management
7. Actual Cost/ collection incurred is taken from the unaudited provisional books of accounts as at 31st May, 2022.
8. Figures have been rounded off to the nearest rupee.
